library(tidyr)
data <- read.csv("owid-covid-data.csv")

data <- data %>% mutate(cases = total_cases_per_million,
                        deaths = total_deaths_per_million,
                        vac1 = people_vaccinated,
                        vac2 = people_fully_vaccinated,
                        pop = population)

data <- data %>% select(continent,
                        location,
                        date,
                        cases,
                        deaths,
                        vac1,
                        vac2)
